data.title: Anurekha Deb
data.description: Hi, I can make decent meals (in fact, delicious sometimes) and I would love to cook and send to people who are suffering from COVID anywhere in Guwahati, as many aren’t able to cook due to numerous reasons. Nutrition is our basic need and I know how testing can such times be when you are unwell and at your most vulnerable self. I want to cook and send nutritious meals which might help people suffering from COVID get proper nutrition and recover faster. I would urge you to share this amongst people who might need it, and also to share this amongst people who might want to collaborate with me in this in terms of donation/ providing transportation means for food delivery or in anything they feel they can help. People with COVID having pets in their homes can also request for meals for their furry babies. We need to take care of each other, we are a community and we need to work together while maintaining physical distance, not social.
